the number of unique music

00:04:46.570 --> 00:04:51.210
tracks in the world,
unique-- so they are unique

00:04:51.210 --> 00:04:55.340
just once in an album--
it's around 4 million.

00:04:55.340 --> 00:05:02.115
Out of that, 60% of them
are mainly English track.

00:05:02.115 --> 00:05:07.760
But then there's a huge, long
tail with Spanish, Chinese,

00:05:07.760 --> 00:05:13.060
Japanese, Indian, Portuguese,
Italian, German, French,

00:05:13.060 --> 00:05:13.750
and whatever.

00:05:13.750 --> 00:05:17.280
So we have actually-- you
know we're a database--

00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:21.400
we do cover-- we have to cover,
so for us, the localization

00:05:21.400 --> 00:05:23.690
is a must.

00:05:23.690 --> 00:05:27.480
I mean, we do cover more
than 80 different languages,

00:05:27.480 --> 00:05:29.490
in terms of content.

00:05:29.490 --> 00:05:32.240
So the challenge for
us is-- Musixmatch

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:33.870
is a crowd-sourced platform.

00:05:33.870 --> 00:05:37.400
So the more we
grow in a country,

00:05:37.400 --> 00:05:39.840
the more-- you
mentioned Japan before.

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:42.020
Japan, it's been incredibly
important for us,

00:05:42.020 --> 00:05:43.690
because the more we
were growing there,

00:05:43.690 --> 00:05:47.210
the more the Japanese users
were adding the content.

00:05:47.210 --> 00:05:49.100
So we give the
power to the users

00:05:49.100 --> 00:05:51.180
to add the localized content.

00:05:53.870 --> 00:05:57.030
So what I want to
share is that, if you

00:05:57.030 --> 00:06:01.630
run content inside your
app, whatever you do,

00:06:01.630 --> 00:06:05.680
from lyrics, whatever, your
content must be localized,

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:06.550
must be offered.

00:06:06.550 --> 00:06:09.060
Which doesn't mean, as you
say, just translate your app.

00:06:09.060 --> 00:06:12.600
You have the issue of
offering your local content.

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:18.100
Brazilian, typically, they
like certain kind of music,

00:06:18.100 --> 00:06:20.290
different from German people.

00:06:20.290 --> 00:06:23.930
And US, different
from Japanese people.

00:06:23.930 --> 00:06:29.340
So for us, it's really a must
to get the local content,

00:06:29.340 --> 00:06:31.240
plus ensuring the local rights.

00:06:31.240 --> 00:06:34.310
Because we pay rights
holder in every single place

00:06:34.310 --> 00:06:36.480
of the world, you know?

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:41.330
But I must say that it's kind
of key challenge and strategy

00:06:41.330 --> 00:06:42.160
for us.

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:48.630
Without that, we couldn't really
be present in any country.

00:06:48.630 --> 00:06:52.820
Like, for us, being in Japan
without having Japanese lyrics,

00:06:52.820 --> 00:06:53.770
it's kind of--

