00:07:03.500 --> 00:07:05.999
HIROTAKA YOSHITSUGU: I mean,
application-- store listing.

00:07:05.999 --> 00:07:07.790
MASSIMO CIOCIOLA: I
mean, we don't localize

00:07:07.790 --> 00:07:09.090
