we built a strategy

00:10:22.630 --> 00:10:25.110
with the Google Play
team and, of course,

00:10:25.110 --> 00:10:26.680
with our marketing team.

00:10:26.680 --> 00:10:30.270
And gradually, we started in--
we're located in Tel Aviv,

00:10:30.270 --> 00:10:32.710
Israel-- so we
started in Israel.

00:10:32.710 --> 00:10:35.040
And then, we started
to grow in Singapore,

00:10:35.040 --> 00:10:39.180
in Malaysia, in Thailand, and
all around Southeast Asia,

00:10:39.180 --> 00:10:41.400
