00:13:57.481 --> 00:14:01.865
j changing icons globally,
like for localized markets,

00:14:01.865 --> 00:14:07.930
do you guys ever worry about
keeping a consistent brand

00:14:07.930 --> 00:14:09.320
for your developer company?

00:14:09.320 --> 00:14:11.320
Is this something that
you guys have dealt with?

00:14:11.320 --> 00:14:13.480
MALE SPEAKER: You mean
changing the brand?

00:14:13.480 --> 00:14:14.220
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:14:14.220 --> 00:14:17.340
If you change the
icon, it can obviously

00:14:17.340 --> 00:14:19.325
change the perception
of the brand,

00:14:19.325 --> 00:14:21.360
