00:17:12.829 --> 00:17:14.839
But when we do these
kind of changes,

00:17:14.839 --> 00:17:16.579
we are worried about the brand.

00:17:16.579 --> 00:17:17.740
I mean, is a good point.

00:17:17.740 --> 00:17:21.319
So we try to maintain
the essence of the icon,

00:17:21.319 --> 00:17:25.319
keeping the core of the
icon, and adding a loop,

00:17:25.319 --> 00:17:28.500
saying to the users, hey, there
is something new in the game.

00:17:28.500 --> 00:17:32.557
So we take care of the brand,
making changes on the icon,

00:17:32.557 --> 00:17:33.140
but carefully.

