00:18:47.890 --> 00:18:51.560
So we have done
changes on pricing.

00:18:51.560 --> 00:18:55.760
We have seen improvements
from 10% to 25%

00:18:55.760 --> 00:18:57.860
in some regions
and some markets.

00:18:57.860 --> 00:19:03.860
So I would say it's
important to have the prices.

00:19:03.860 --> 00:19:05.990
I wouldn't do it
at the beginning.

00:19:05.990 --> 00:19:10.100
I would launch the game,
see which is the ARPPU,

00:19:10.100 --> 00:19:11.800
the A-R-P-P-U, that
you are seeing,

00:19:11.800 --> 00:19:14.996
and then do improvements to try
to boost revenues by 10%, 15%,

00:19:14.996 --> 00:19:17.226
20% of [INAUDIBLE].

00:19:17.226 --> 00:19:19.290
REGINA CHAMMA:
Just to add here, I

00:19:19.290 --> 00:19:22.920
