is something new

00:19:26.280 --> 00:19:27.280
in the emerging markets.

00:19:27.280 --> 00:19:29.682
I'm not talking only for
Brazil and Latin America,

00:19:29.682 --> 00:19:30.890
but all the emerging markets.

00:19:30.890 --> 00:19:33.220
Google actually is
investing quite a lot.

00:19:33.220 --> 00:19:36.220
We are putting not only the
technology there, but really

00:19:36.220 --> 00:19:37.172
people there.

00:19:37.172 --> 00:19:38.630
We are spending
consumer marketing.

00:19:38.630 --> 00:19:41.990
We are really educating these
users to buy digital goods.

00:19:41.990 --> 00:19:43.690
We are not in Japan,
that people are

00:19:43.690 --> 00:19:47.010
used to buy digital
goods-- or US, or UK.

00:19:47.010 --> 00:19:49.970
These people are just learning
how to use smart phones

00:19:49.970 --> 00:19:54.830
and engage with digital
goods, or games, or apps,

00:19:54.830 --> 00:19:57.380
so we need actually
to educate that.

00:19:57.380 --> 00:20:01.119
We just launched local forms of
payments in Brazil and Mexico,

00:20:01.119 --> 00:20:01.660
for instance.

00:20:01.660 --> 00:20:04.210
So until last year,
we didn't have--

00:20:04.210 --> 00:20:07.179
