were accepted in the store.

00:20:07.179 --> 00:20:09.720
So this is something that-- it's
a big [INAUDIBLE] that we've

00:20:09.720 --> 00:20:12.710
been doing, not only in Latin
America, but all the emerging

00:20:12.710 --> 00:20:13.620
markets.

00:20:13.620 --> 00:20:17.550
And we're going to be pushing
that, educating the users.

00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:22.330
But I definitely believe
changing prices, specifically

00:20:22.330 --> 00:20:24.860
for some markets, are important.

00:20:24.860 --> 00:20:27.810
