00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:40.160
Is that a market there
that I have to explore?

00:20:40.160 --> 00:20:47.520
And if yes, try to find out
what is the right pricing point.

00:20:47.520 --> 00:20:49.980
What is the user behavior of
that market, should really

00:20:49.980 --> 00:20:51.317
be your strategy.

00:20:51.317 --> 00:20:52.900
But this is something
that we're going

00:20:52.900 --> 00:20:56.790
